		"description": "<p><em>Passive: Whenever you roll initiative, you and each ally within 60 feet gain a bonus to initiative equal to your proficiency bonus.</em></p><p><em><strong>Legend Dice Feature</strong></em><strong> — Shout of the Story:</strong> As a bonus action, expend a Legend Die to rally nearby allies. Each ally within 15 feet gains temporary hit points equal to the result and an expertise die on their next saving throw made before the end of their next turn.</p>",
